ion: absolute; clip: rect(1.26em 1002.46em 2.626em -999.997em); top: -2.183em; left: 0.003em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-446"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-447" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">S<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.057em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-448" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">[</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-449" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">i</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-450" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">]</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-451" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">[</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-452" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">j</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-453" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">]</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.189em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.397em; border-left-width: 0px; border-left-style: solid; width: 0px; height: 1.337em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>S</mi><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy="false">]</mo><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><mi>j</mi><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-55">S[i][j]</script> có thể được tính từ trái sang phải, từ trên xuống dưới, hoặc từ trên xuống, từ trái sang.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Mã giả:</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>For i = 0 to N - 1\n   For j = 0 to M - 1\n   S[i][j] = A[i][j] +\n      max(S[i][j-1], if j&gt;0 ; S[i-1][j], if i&gt;0 ; 0)\n\nOutput S[n-1][m-1]\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>Ví dụ khác:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n<a href="http://community.topcoder.com/tc?module=ProblemDetail&amp;rd=4709&amp;pm=1889">AvoidRoads</a> – 2003 TCO Semifinals 4</li>\n  <li>\n<a href="http://community.topcoder.com/tc?module=ProblemDetail&amp;rd=4482&amp;pm=1592">ChessMetric</a> – 2003 TCCC Round 4</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h1><a class="anchor" id="upper-intermediate" href="#upper-intermediate"><i class="fa fa-link"></i></a>Upper-Intermediate</h1>\n\n<p>Phần này sẽ giới thiệu với bạn những bài toán cùng với một số điều kiện.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Đây là một ví dụ cụ thể:</strong></p>\n\n<p>Cho đồ thị vô hướng <span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-56-Frame" tabindex="0" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>G</mi></math>" role="presentation" style="position: relative;"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-454" role="math" style="width: 1.041em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.822em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.314em 1000.82em 2.352em -999.997em); top: -2.183em; left: 0.003em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-455"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-456" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">G</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.189em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.063em; border-left-width: 0px; border-left-style: solid; width: 0px; height: 1.003em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>G</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-56">G</script> có trọng số dương và <span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-57-Frame" tabindex="0" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>N</mi></math>" role="presentation" style="position: relative;"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-457" role="math" style="width: 1.15em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-